---
title: One-Pot Sausage and Tortelloni Soup with Baby Spinach in a Tomato Broth
description: Give the dishwasher a break tonight: all you need to put this recipe together is a pot and a couple utensils for stirring and chopping. But just because it involves minimal effort doesn’t mean that it has minimal flavor. Loaded with cheesy tortelloni, slices of sweet sausage, tender spinach leaves, and a tomato-y broth, the soup brims and bubbles with plenty of filling, Italian-inspired flavors.
